1
00:01:49,060 --> 00:01:54,580
=Eight Hundred=

2
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:01,420
Now that you're technically recovered,

3
00:02:02,190 --> 00:02:03,580
there's something I need to ask you.

4
00:02:04,910 --> 00:02:05,860
What is it, Dad?

5
00:02:07,220 --> 00:02:08,550
The day of your accident,

6
00:02:09,110 --> 00:02:09,950
what exactly

7
00:02:10,670 --> 00:02:11,740
did Huo Kaiming say to you?

8
00:02:13,070 --> 00:02:13,910
Yes,

9
00:02:17,830 --> 00:02:18,740
what did he say?

10
00:02:21,020 --> 00:02:22,350
Chen Hongbing,

11
00:02:22,350 --> 00:02:23,190
what are you doing?

12
00:02:24,620 --> 00:02:26,110
Hui went through so much.

13
00:02:26,860 --> 00:02:28,740
As his father, is it wrong

14
00:02:28,740 --> 00:02:29,600
for me to ask?

15
00:02:29,610 --> 00:02:30,700
Enough already.

16
00:02:31,130 --> 00:02:32,300
Don't you know Hui's illness

17
00:02:32,300 --> 00:02:33,230
was triggered

18
00:02:33,230 --> 00:02:34,270
by emotional stress?

19
00:02:34,270 --> 00:02:35,310
Do you want him to relapse?

20
00:02:35,860 --> 00:02:37,350
He'll relapse just because I asked?

21
00:02:37,860 --> 00:02:38,790
I'm telling you,

22
00:02:38,790 --> 00:02:39,950
if anything happens to Hui,

23
00:02:40,420 --> 00:02:41,620
I'll be coming for you.

24
00:02:42,220 --> 00:02:43,460
Is it necessary to be so harsh?

25
00:02:43,830 --> 00:02:45,390
Fine, I won't ask. Happy now?

26
00:02:45,580 --> 00:02:47,070
Every single day,

27
00:02:47,070 --> 00:02:47,950
pinch, pinch...

28
00:02:47,950 --> 00:02:49,300
Hui, it's okay.

29
00:02:49,300 --> 00:02:50,420
Don't think about it anymore.

30
00:02:50,420 --> 00:02:51,270
Just forget it.

31
00:02:51,270 --> 00:02:52,350
Now that you're back,

32
00:02:52,350 --> 00:02:53,700
the whole family is here.

33
00:02:53,700 --> 00:02:54,900
No one dares to hurt you now.

34
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:56,840
- Okay, Mom.
- Think of something happy.

35
00:02:58,350 --> 00:02:59,460
Here, have some celery.

36
00:02:59,460 --> 00:03:00,300
Thanks.

37
00:03:03,270 --> 00:03:04,110
What's that smell?

38
00:03:06,790 --> 00:03:07,830
My mutton!

39
00:03:07,830 --> 00:03:09,030
- Songge, help me!
- Okay.

40
00:03:09,810 --> 00:03:10,670
Still pinching me?

41
00:03:10,670 --> 00:03:11,510
Look.

42
00:03:12,640 --> 00:03:13,560
Songge.

43
00:03:13,580 --> 00:03:15,100
- I'll get the water.
- Hurry, get some water!

44
00:03:15,110 --> 00:03:15,950
Okay.

45
00:03:18,390 --> 00:03:20,270
This is a total waste of my cooking.

46
00:03:21,350 --> 00:03:22,830
It smells great to me.

47
00:03:22,830 --> 00:03:23,770
I'm sure it's delicious.

48
00:03:30,620 --> 00:03:31,460
Songge,

49
00:03:33,140 --> 00:03:33,980
there's something

50
00:03:35,350 --> 00:03:37,700
that's been weighing on my heart.

51
00:03:38,700 --> 00:03:39,540
I think

52
00:03:40,950 --> 00:03:42,230
I should talk to you about it.

53
00:03:43,070 --> 00:03:44,140
What is it, Mrs. Chen?

54
00:03:45,580 --> 00:03:47,110
I want to apologize to you.

55
00:03:49,300 --> 00:03:50,860
About that day at the hospital,

56
00:03:52,180 --> 00:03:53,670
when I told you to leave Hui.

57
00:03:54,900 --> 00:03:56,180
I was being inconsiderate.

58
00:03:56,830 --> 00:03:57,830
I was wrong.

59
00:03:58,620 --> 00:03:59,580
These past few days,

60
00:04:00,300 --> 00:04:02,300
you've cared for Hui day and night.

61
00:04:02,990 --> 00:04:04,580
I've seen it all,

62
00:04:05,270 --> 00:04:06,180
and I feel for you.

63
00:04:14,550 --> 00:04:15,620
Songge,

64
00:04:15,620 --> 00:04:16,990
can you forgive me?

65
00:04:28,860 --> 00:04:29,700
Mrs. Chen,

66
00:04:30,860 --> 00:04:32,350
I never blamed you.

67
00:04:34,420 --> 00:04:35,420
Actually,

68
00:04:37,150 --> 00:04:38,500
I've always felt

69
00:04:38,500 --> 00:04:40,260
really bad toward you and Mr. Chen.

70
00:04:41,590 --> 00:04:42,990
All these years,

71
00:04:42,990 --> 00:04:44,590
you both worked so hard to raise me.

72
00:04:46,230 --> 00:04:47,860
I wanted to grow up

73
00:04:47,860 --> 00:04:48,910
and properly repay you.

74
00:04:50,710 --> 00:04:51,550
But instead,

75
00:04:52,620 --> 00:04:54,150
I ended up getting this illness

76
00:04:54,150 --> 00:04:55,060
and burdened everyone.

77
00:04:55,550 --> 00:04:57,180
I'm the one who dragged you down.

78
00:04:57,180 --> 00:04:58,830
Look at you, silly child.

79
00:04:59,620 --> 00:05:01,420
What kind of nonsense is that?

80
00:05:02,110 --> 00:05:03,470
Getting sick isn't your fault.

81
00:05:06,350 --> 00:05:07,550
I just hope...

82
00:05:09,350 --> 00:05:10,740
I hope our whole family

83
00:05:11,940 --> 00:05:13,180
can be happy and well.

84
00:05:20,860 --> 00:05:21,700
Good girl.

85
00:05:23,670 --> 00:05:25,350
We'll all be just fine.

86
00:05:41,470 --> 00:05:43,830
Dad, here's a toast to you.

87
00:05:44,590 --> 00:05:45,590
Don't be ridiculous.

88
00:05:46,220 --> 00:05:48,150
You haven't recovered yet,
so how can you drink?

89
00:05:48,150 --> 00:05:48,990
Just this one glass.

90
00:05:49,790 --> 00:05:50,670
I want to toast you.

91
00:05:54,550 --> 00:05:55,390
What's wrong?

92
00:05:56,380 --> 00:05:57,590
You've been so busy for me,

93
00:05:58,130 --> 00:05:59,110
worrying yourselves sick.

94
00:05:59,820 --> 00:06:00,670
I've let you down.

95
00:06:08,030 --> 00:06:09,820
Why are you saying this to me?

96
00:06:10,230 --> 00:06:11,230
You're my son.

97
00:06:12,380 --> 00:06:13,620
Your mother and I

98
00:06:13,620 --> 00:06:14,460
looking after you

99
00:06:15,350 --> 00:06:16,940
is only natural.

100
00:06:16,940 --> 00:06:18,380
There's no need for apologies.

101
00:06:21,620 --> 00:06:22,740
Lately,

102
00:06:24,260 --> 00:06:25,590
I've been in a daze.

103
00:06:26,910 --> 00:06:28,150
Every day feels like a dream.

104
00:06:30,710 --> 00:06:31,940
I even saw you crying.

105
00:06:33,670 --> 00:06:34,910
That's nonsense.

106
00:06:35,550 --> 00:06:36,910
Why would I cry?

107
00:06:38,740 --> 00:06:39,580
Tell me.

108
00:06:41,990 --> 00:06:42,830
Are you okay?

109
00:06:46,060 --> 00:06:46,900
I'm fine.

110
00:06:58,180 --> 00:06:59,470
Don't think too much.

111
00:07:01,030 --> 00:07:02,350
Focus on getting better.

112
00:07:03,310 --> 00:07:04,740
That's more important than anything.

113
00:07:10,910 --> 00:07:12,770
The mutton is ready.

114
00:07:13,510 --> 00:07:14,500
Come on, quick.

115
00:07:14,500 --> 00:07:15,710
You mom finished making dinner.

116
00:07:15,820 --> 00:07:17,670
Coming.

117
00:07:20,550 --> 00:07:21,420
Careful, it's hot.

118
00:07:22,820 --> 00:07:24,260
- Hurry and try my cooking.
- Here.

119
00:07:24,260 --> 00:07:26,300
Move a bit closer to Grandpa.

120
00:07:26,300 --> 00:07:27,300
I can reach it.

121
00:07:27,340 --> 00:07:32,180
(Yingxiong Roller Skating Rink)

122
00:07:34,710 --> 00:07:35,550
Chen Hui,

123
00:07:36,620 --> 00:07:39,030
today has been the happiest day
I've had in a long time.

124
00:07:39,790 --> 00:07:40,630
Songge,

125
00:07:42,060 --> 00:07:43,300
let's start over.

126
00:07:45,740 --> 00:07:46,860
Starting over?

127
00:07:48,940 --> 00:07:49,780
I've been thinking.

128
00:07:50,110 --> 00:07:51,710
We can't sell the cough syrup anymore.

129
00:07:52,820 --> 00:07:53,820
And I don't want to run

130
00:07:54,220 --> 00:07:55,510
the roller skating rink anymore.

131
00:07:55,910 --> 00:07:57,350
Is it because of Mr. Chen?

132
00:07:57,350 --> 00:07:58,190
Yes.

133
00:07:58,500 --> 00:07:59,860
This was wrong from the start.

134
00:08:00,940 --> 00:08:02,470
If we keep selling it,

135
00:08:02,470 --> 00:08:04,060
we won't have a home left.

136
00:08:04,060 --> 00:08:05,740
While there's still time,

137
00:08:05,740 --> 00:08:06,790
let's go somewhere else

138
00:08:06,790 --> 00:08:07,710
and start fresh.

139
00:08:08,420 --> 00:08:10,260
If we don't do the roller skating rink,

140
00:08:10,260 --> 00:08:11,500
what will we do for a living?

141
00:08:14,420 --> 00:08:16,210
I want to open
an internet cafe in the city.

142
00:08:17,030 --> 00:08:17,910
An internet cafe?

143
00:08:17,910 --> 00:08:18,750
Yes.

144
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:20,490
I've thought about it for a long time.

145
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:22,420
Young people love
going to internet cafes now.

146
00:08:22,420 --> 00:08:23,790
And there's only one in the city.

147
00:08:24,550 --> 00:08:25,860
I think it's an opportunity.

148
00:08:26,300 --> 00:08:27,300
But Chen Hui,

149
00:08:27,300 --> 00:08:28,940
we still have
a batch of stock out there.

150
00:08:30,110 --> 00:08:31,280
Since we've decided to quit,

151
00:08:31,670 --> 00:08:32,900
we won't want the stock.

152
00:08:32,900 --> 00:08:33,990
Once the heat dies down,

153
00:08:34,640 --> 00:08:36,070
we can just dispose of it then.

154
00:08:38,590 --> 00:08:39,430
Okay.

155
00:08:40,310 --> 00:08:41,860
Since you've made up your mind,

156
00:08:41,860 --> 00:08:42,700
I support you.

157
00:08:49,900 --> 00:08:50,740
Songge,

158
00:08:51,860 --> 00:08:52,700
close your eyes.

159
00:08:53,950 --> 00:08:55,430
Why should I close my eyes?

160
00:08:55,430 --> 00:08:56,380
Just do as I say.

161
00:08:56,380 --> 00:08:57,220
Close your eyes.

162
00:08:59,110 --> 00:09:00,070
Stand up slowly.

163
00:09:03,020 --> 00:09:03,860
Give me your hands.

164
00:09:04,590 --> 00:09:05,430
Slowly.

165
00:09:07,430 --> 00:09:08,280
Where are we going?

166
00:09:08,350 --> 00:09:09,190
Careful now.

167
00:09:12,470 --> 00:09:13,310
Alright.

168
00:09:14,860 --> 00:09:16,190
No peeking.

169
00:09:19,230 --> 00:09:20,190
You can look now.

170
00:09:31,140 --> 00:09:32,260
It's so beautiful.

171
00:09:33,380 --> 00:09:34,380
What fish is this?

172
00:09:35,590 --> 00:09:37,020
They're called Pterophyllum.

173
00:09:37,020 --> 00:09:38,110
Some call them angelfish.

174
00:09:39,190 --> 00:09:40,260
So pretty.

175
00:09:42,230 --> 00:09:43,590
Pterophyllum.

176
00:09:47,350 --> 00:09:48,190
I hope we can be

177
00:09:48,210 --> 00:09:49,350
as happy as they are.

178
00:09:53,780 --> 00:09:54,620
We will be.

179
00:09:57,420 --> 00:10:01,220
=Episode 10=
(A New Beginning)

180
00:10:07,060 --> 00:10:08,420
(People's Public Security)

181
00:10:08,430 --> 00:10:10,110
There is some good news

182
00:10:10,110 --> 00:10:11,540
to announce to everyone today.

183
00:10:11,540 --> 00:10:13,660
Regarding the case
handled by our station and the Criminal

184
00:10:13,660 --> 00:10:14,990
Investigations Brigade
of the municipal PSB,

185
00:10:14,990 --> 00:10:16,950
the Zhang Mei, Yu Susu, and Jiao Yuqin

186
00:10:16,950 --> 00:10:18,500
"Death Benefit Bride" gang case,

187
00:10:18,500 --> 00:10:19,430
the court

188
00:10:19,430 --> 00:10:20,660
has already reached a verdict.

189
00:10:21,350 --> 00:10:23,350
For this, the bureau
leadership has awarded

190
00:10:23,350 --> 00:10:26,140
our station
a Collective Second-Class Merit.

191
00:10:26,140 --> 00:10:28,260
This is the highest commendation

192
00:10:28,260 --> 00:10:30,350
we've received
since our station was founded.

193
00:10:30,350 --> 00:10:31,470
- Great!
- Excellent!

194
00:10:32,700 --> 00:10:35,140
(Fengyang Town Police Station, Jiangbin City.
Collective Second-Class Merit. Honorary Credential)

195
00:10:36,350 --> 00:10:38,590
Although the bureau leadership
has given our station

196
00:10:38,590 --> 00:10:39,950
such high praise,

197
00:10:39,950 --> 00:10:41,500
none of us can afford

198
00:10:41,500 --> 00:10:42,470
to let our guard down.

199
00:10:42,470 --> 00:10:43,710
For instance, Huo Kaiming,

200
00:10:43,710 --> 00:10:45,470
who committed the body-burning homicide,

201
00:10:45,470 --> 00:10:46,430
is still at large.

202
00:10:46,430 --> 00:10:48,020
The scarred woman
selling the cough syrup

203
00:10:48,020 --> 00:10:49,020
hasn't been found yet either.

204
00:10:49,020 --> 00:10:51,140
So I hope that you keep working hard

205
00:10:51,140 --> 00:10:52,740
to strive for a First-Class Merit.

206
00:10:52,740 --> 00:10:53,710
- Good.
- Good.

207
00:10:56,590 --> 00:10:57,430
Hongbing,

208
00:10:58,070 --> 00:11:00,470
how is the investigation
over at the water treatment plant?

209
00:11:01,780 --> 00:11:02,860
It's like this.

210
00:11:02,860 --> 00:11:03,830
Over the past week,

211
00:11:03,830 --> 00:11:05,710
we have visited every single

212
00:11:06,260 --> 00:11:07,620
water treatment plant

213
00:11:07,620 --> 00:11:09,020
around Fengyang.

214
00:11:09,500 --> 00:11:10,470
The polyacrylamide

215
00:11:10,470 --> 00:11:11,710
that Tang mentioned

216
00:11:11,710 --> 00:11:13,430
is actually used by the plants

217
00:11:13,430 --> 00:11:15,620
to treat sludge sedimentation.

218
00:11:16,070 --> 00:11:17,740
We requested

219
00:11:17,740 --> 00:11:19,230
the list of employees who have access

220
00:11:19,230 --> 00:11:20,190
to this substance,

221
00:11:20,190 --> 00:11:21,950
but we found that none of them

222
00:11:21,950 --> 00:11:23,740
have had any contact with Huo Kaiming.

223
00:11:23,740 --> 00:11:24,590
In fact, none of them

224
00:11:24,590 --> 00:11:26,260
even has a criminal record.

225
00:11:26,260 --> 00:11:28,020
This is what's giving us

226
00:11:28,020 --> 00:11:29,140
a headache right now.

227
00:11:29,140 --> 00:11:30,590
How is the investigation

228
00:11:30,590 --> 00:11:31,830
into Huo Kaiming going?

229
00:11:31,830 --> 00:11:32,670
Director Tong,

230
00:11:33,230 --> 00:11:34,260
after Chen Hui woke up,

231
00:11:34,260 --> 00:11:35,950
he came to the station.

232
00:11:35,950 --> 00:11:36,860
He gave a statement

233
00:11:36,860 --> 00:11:38,260
about the day Huo Kaiming escaped,

234
00:11:38,260 --> 00:11:39,860
recounting what happened.

235
00:11:39,860 --> 00:11:40,710
It's basically consistent with

236
00:11:40,710 --> 00:11:41,830
what Gao Songge and the owner

237
00:11:41,830 --> 00:11:43,310
of the photo studio said.

238
00:11:43,310 --> 00:11:44,470
Rest assured,

239
00:11:44,470 --> 00:11:45,540
we set up surveillance

240
00:11:45,540 --> 00:11:46,470
at every station

241
00:11:46,470 --> 00:11:47,830
where the coal train

242
00:11:47,830 --> 00:11:48,860
passed during his escape.

243
00:11:49,310 --> 00:11:50,830
However, at Linchuan Station,

244
00:11:50,830 --> 00:11:53,020
Huo Kaiming's blood was found
in the nearby bushes.

245
00:11:53,020 --> 00:11:55,540
At that time, we conducted
a joint search operation

246
00:11:55,540 --> 00:11:57,070
with the local police,

247
00:11:57,070 --> 00:11:58,660
but we couldn't find him.

248
00:11:58,660 --> 00:11:59,950
Given the current situation,

249
00:11:59,950 --> 00:12:01,190
I suspect that Huo Kaiming

250
00:12:01,190 --> 00:12:03,190
is either already dead,

251
00:12:03,190 --> 00:12:04,500
or he has escaped to

252
00:12:04,500 --> 00:12:05,660
a neighboring province.

253
00:12:07,230 --> 00:12:08,350
Limin,

254
00:12:08,350 --> 00:12:09,310
share this information

255
00:12:09,310 --> 00:12:10,500
with the surrounding provinces

256
00:12:10,500 --> 00:12:11,860
so they can stay synced.

257
00:12:11,860 --> 00:12:13,500
Tell them to give us

258
00:12:13,500 --> 00:12:15,190
timely feedback on any news.

259
00:12:15,190 --> 00:12:16,030
Understood.

260
00:12:16,590 --> 00:12:18,260
Keep up the good work.

261
00:12:18,260 --> 00:12:20,110
That's all for today's meeting.

262
00:12:20,230 --> 00:12:21,070
Meeting adjourned.

263
00:12:22,780 --> 00:12:24,660
(There is no way out for violations.
Reform through hard work for a new life)

264
00:12:33,020 --> 00:12:33,860
Hui,

265
00:12:33,990 --> 00:12:34,950
what are you doing here?

266
00:12:34,950 --> 00:12:35,830
Mr. Huang,

267
00:12:35,830 --> 00:12:36,900
I'm here to see you.

268
00:12:36,900 --> 00:12:38,380
I topped up some money on your card.

269
00:12:40,070 --> 00:12:41,500
Why be so polite with me?

270
00:12:41,500 --> 00:12:42,710
Mr. Huang,

271
00:12:42,710 --> 00:12:44,350
I want to start a business,

272
00:12:44,350 --> 00:12:45,540
and I want you to invest.

273
00:12:47,190 --> 00:12:48,350
Me? Invest?

274
00:12:48,350 --> 00:12:49,950
Look at my situation now.

275
00:12:49,950 --> 00:12:50,790
How can I invest?

276
00:12:51,230 --> 00:12:52,620
You just need to provide the funds.

277
00:12:53,140 --> 00:12:54,470
Is this your father's idea?

278
00:12:54,470 --> 00:12:56,020
It has nothing to do with him.

279
00:12:56,020 --> 00:12:56,990
It's my idea.

280
00:12:57,830 --> 00:12:58,780
Mr. Huang,

281
00:12:58,780 --> 00:12:59,710
there's a new thing

282
00:12:59,710 --> 00:13:02,010
in the big cities now
called an internet cafe.

283
00:13:02,020 --> 00:13:02,710
You use a computer

284
00:13:02,720 --> 00:13:04,500
to chat with strangers
from all over the country.

285
00:13:04,500 --> 00:13:05,950
I've researched the market.

286
00:13:05,950 --> 00:13:07,990
Right now, there's only one
in the whole city,

287
00:13:07,990 --> 00:13:08,990
and it's packed every day.

288
00:13:08,990 --> 00:13:10,350
You can't even get in line.

289
00:13:10,350 --> 00:13:12,660
If we can open one,
it will make money for sure.

290
00:13:13,620 --> 00:13:14,660
Wait,

291
00:13:14,660 --> 00:13:16,350
you can make money just by chatting?

292
00:13:16,350 --> 00:13:17,230
Yeah.

293
00:13:17,230 --> 00:13:18,990
I wouldn't believe it
if I hadn't seen it myself.

294
00:13:18,990 --> 00:13:19,900
Once those young guys

295
00:13:19,900 --> 00:13:20,800
get on,

296
00:13:20,810 --> 00:13:21,660
they play all night.

297
00:13:21,660 --> 00:13:22,740
They don't sleep at all.

298
00:13:24,310 --> 00:13:25,260
Computers...

299
00:13:25,260 --> 00:13:26,500
I've heard of them too.

300
00:13:27,380 --> 00:13:28,990
But can you actually

301
00:13:28,990 --> 00:13:30,260
figure out those things?

302
00:13:30,260 --> 00:13:32,590
I've already sent
Han to Beijing to learn.

303
00:13:32,590 --> 00:13:34,430
If others can figure it out, so can we.

304
00:13:37,780 --> 00:13:38,860
How much do you need?

305
00:13:39,540 --> 00:13:41,110
I'll put in 100,000.

306
00:13:41,110 --> 00:13:42,190
Mr. Huang,

307
00:13:42,190 --> 00:13:43,830
I'd like you to put in 200,000.

308
00:13:43,830 --> 00:13:45,260
We'll split the profits 50-50.

309
00:13:45,260 --> 00:13:46,100
200,000?

310
00:13:49,140 --> 00:13:49,990
That's a lot.

311
00:13:49,990 --> 00:13:52,660
Mr. Huang, this makes way more
than the roller skating rink.

312
00:13:52,660 --> 00:13:53,830
And there's no risk.

313
00:13:54,660 --> 00:13:56,830
I could actually scrape it together,

314
00:13:56,830 --> 00:13:58,070
but then I'd have to use

315
00:13:58,070 --> 00:13:59,500
Gao Songge's kidney transplant money.

316
00:13:59,820 --> 00:14:00,780
That's why I'm planning

317
00:14:00,780 --> 00:14:01,900
to give up half the shares.

318
00:14:02,430 --> 00:14:03,900
I just want to invest less capital.

319
00:14:06,380 --> 00:14:07,220
Fine.

320
00:14:07,710 --> 00:14:08,550
I'm in.

321
00:14:09,660 --> 00:14:11,350
Okay, when you go back,

322
00:14:11,350 --> 00:14:12,470
go see my sister.

323
00:14:12,920 --> 00:14:14,140
Tell her to come over tomorrow.

324
00:14:15,070 --> 00:14:15,910
Okay.

325
00:14:16,470 --> 00:14:17,540
Mr. Huang,

326
00:14:17,540 --> 00:14:18,380
don't tell my dad

327
00:14:18,900 --> 00:14:19,990
about this.

328
00:14:19,990 --> 00:14:21,190
If he finds out,

329
00:14:21,190 --> 00:14:22,140
he'll chew me out.

330
00:14:25,830 --> 00:14:26,900
Look at you.

331
00:14:26,900 --> 00:14:28,140
We two officers are acting

332
00:14:28,140 --> 00:14:29,950
like thieves who are sneaking around.

333
00:14:29,950 --> 00:14:32,590
Master, it's about
my transfer to the municipal PSB.

334
00:14:33,140 --> 00:14:33,980
It's almost settled.

335
00:14:34,350 --> 00:14:35,810
Just waiting for the official notice.

336
00:14:36,430 --> 00:14:37,270
When are you leaving?

337
00:14:38,140 --> 00:14:39,350
In the next few days.

338
00:14:39,350 --> 00:14:41,260
I've been by your side
for so many years,

339
00:14:41,260 --> 00:14:42,140
learning so much.

340
00:14:42,140 --> 00:14:43,990
I wanted you to be the first to know.

341
00:14:43,990 --> 00:14:45,470
You little rascal.

342
00:14:46,230 --> 00:14:47,350
Impressive.

343
00:14:47,350 --> 00:14:48,190
So you're leaving.

344
00:14:50,380 --> 00:14:52,900
When I first started at this station,

345
00:14:52,900 --> 00:14:53,830
my son, Hui,

346
00:14:53,830 --> 00:14:54,900
was still in high school.

347
00:14:55,710 --> 00:14:56,650
In the blink of an eye,

348
00:14:57,260 --> 00:14:58,110
your wings have grown.

349
00:14:58,710 --> 00:14:59,550
You're ready to fly.

350
00:15:00,350 --> 00:15:01,990
Master, why would you say that?

351
00:15:01,990 --> 00:15:04,020
You're making me
feel like I'm not a good son.

352
00:15:04,020 --> 00:15:05,190
Look at yourself.

353
00:15:06,590 --> 00:15:07,710
I'm just getting old

354
00:15:07,710 --> 00:15:08,780
and like to nag.

355
00:15:08,780 --> 00:15:09,620
But seeing you

356
00:15:09,630 --> 00:15:11,110
doing so well for yourself,

357
00:15:12,020 --> 00:15:13,190
I'm truly

358
00:15:13,190 --> 00:15:14,030
happy for you.

359
00:15:17,110 --> 00:15:19,380
Master, since I'm leaving,
let me buy you dinner soon.

360
00:15:19,380 --> 00:15:20,220
Forget it.

361
00:15:21,020 --> 00:15:22,110
You're leaving.

362
00:15:22,110 --> 00:15:23,230
We can't have you pay.

363
00:15:24,500 --> 00:15:25,710
Let Director Tong treat.

364
00:15:25,710 --> 00:15:27,950
We'll get everyone together
and give you a proper send-off.

365
00:15:27,950 --> 00:15:29,190
Alright. Master, look,

366
00:15:29,190 --> 00:15:30,140
since I'm leaving,

367
00:15:30,900 --> 00:15:32,430
teach me a few more tricks.

368
00:15:32,430 --> 00:15:33,740
After all, I'm going
to the municipal PSB...

369
00:15:33,740 --> 00:15:35,740
What tricks could I possibly have?

370
00:15:35,740 --> 00:15:37,110
In my whole life,

371
00:15:37,110 --> 00:15:38,830
all I've seen

372
00:15:38,830 --> 00:15:40,110
is this 800-meter radius area.

373
00:15:40,110 --> 00:15:41,860
But you, you're capable.

374
00:15:41,860 --> 00:15:42,860
You've got talent.

375
00:15:43,860 --> 00:15:45,660
But wherever you go, never forget

376
00:15:48,500 --> 00:15:50,190
to always be a good cop.

377
00:15:51,120 --> 00:15:52,900
If you run into trouble
at the municipal PSB,

378
00:15:54,500 --> 00:15:56,020
you can always come to me for advice.

379
00:15:56,620 --> 00:15:58,260
I'm sure about that.

380
00:15:59,230 --> 00:16:00,070
I'm leaving.

381
00:16:05,020 --> 00:16:05,940
Hello, Chief Liu.

382
00:16:06,310 --> 00:16:07,230
Director Chen.

383
00:16:07,230 --> 00:16:08,500
Regarding the Gao Ying case
you mentioned,

384
00:16:08,500 --> 00:16:09,340
after I returned to the city,

385
00:16:09,340 --> 00:16:11,430
(Witness Inquiry Record)
I reviewed the case files from back then.

386
00:16:11,430 --> 00:16:13,990
Conditions were limited at the time,
and no physical evidence

387
00:16:13,990 --> 00:16:15,500
or test data were left behind.

388
00:16:15,500 --> 00:16:16,380
If, as you say,

389
00:16:16,380 --> 00:16:17,220
Gao Ying's death

390
00:16:17,220 --> 00:16:18,660
really is related to Huo Kaiming,

391
00:16:18,660 --> 00:16:20,430
there's only one way to prove it now.

392
00:16:21,590 --> 00:16:23,500
You mean an autopsy?

393
00:16:23,500 --> 00:16:25,310
Yes, but given the current situation,

394
00:16:25,310 --> 00:16:26,990
we still lack direct evidence.

395
00:16:26,990 --> 00:16:28,470
To start the autopsy procedure,

396
00:16:28,470 --> 00:16:30,410
we must have a signature
from Gao Ying's family.

397
00:16:33,780 --> 00:16:34,950
There aren't many

398
00:16:34,950 --> 00:16:36,710
of Gao Ying's relatives left now.

399
00:16:36,710 --> 00:16:38,430
Only Songge is left.

400
00:16:38,430 --> 00:16:39,780
I can take on this task.

401
00:16:41,190 --> 00:16:42,030
Director Chen.

402
00:16:42,920 --> 00:16:45,070
Chief Liu, if you have
something to say, just say it.

403
00:16:46,070 --> 00:16:47,830
Don't you think you should discuss

404
00:16:47,830 --> 00:16:48,710
this matter

405
00:16:48,710 --> 00:16:49,950
with your wife

406
00:16:49,950 --> 00:16:50,790
first?

407
00:16:53,830 --> 00:16:54,830
You're right.

408
00:16:55,500 --> 00:16:56,540
Thank you for the reminder.

409
00:16:57,140 --> 00:16:58,710
In this matter, it really requires

410
00:16:59,230 --> 00:17:00,830
my wife to give the nod first.

411
00:17:01,900 --> 00:17:03,020
That's the safer way.

412
00:17:06,150 --> 00:17:07,260
Dr. Ding, you're back.

413
00:17:07,870 --> 00:17:08,710
I'm back.

414
00:17:33,390 --> 00:17:34,230
I'm back.

415
00:17:35,430 --> 00:17:36,470
Ding Yue, you're back.

416
00:17:36,910 --> 00:17:39,150
Better to arrive at the right time
than to arrive early.

417
00:17:39,150 --> 00:17:40,820
Why does this smell so good?

418
00:17:40,820 --> 00:17:42,190
Look at this.

419
00:17:42,190 --> 00:17:43,640
Wash your hands and get ready to eat.

420
00:17:45,340 --> 00:17:47,540
This is a first.

421
00:17:47,540 --> 00:17:49,580
You've been working too hard lately.

422
00:17:49,580 --> 00:17:52,060
Of course I have to show off my skills
to reward you.

423
00:17:53,060 --> 00:17:53,950
Do you have something

424
00:17:53,950 --> 00:17:54,950
to tell me?

425
00:17:54,950 --> 00:17:55,790
You go first.

426
00:17:55,950 --> 00:17:56,990
Come on,

427
00:17:56,990 --> 00:17:58,950
can't I just care about you?

428
00:17:59,580 --> 00:18:00,740
Please don't do this.

429
00:18:00,740 --> 00:18:01,710
It creeps me out.

430
00:18:01,710 --> 00:18:02,550
Just say it.

431
00:18:04,230 --> 00:18:06,260
Well, nothing gets past you.

432
00:18:07,340 --> 00:18:08,870
There is indeed one thing.

433
00:18:08,870 --> 00:18:09,740
The municipal PSB recently...

434
00:18:09,740 --> 00:18:11,300
Mr. Chen, Mrs. Chen, we're back.

435
00:18:11,300 --> 00:18:12,190
Dad, Mom.

436
00:18:12,190 --> 00:18:13,480
Hui, Songge.

437
00:18:13,480 --> 00:18:14,340
You brought so many things.

438
00:18:14,350 --> 00:18:15,340
My grandson, you're back.

439
00:18:15,780 --> 00:18:17,820
You two, did you follow
your noses back here?

440
00:18:17,820 --> 00:18:19,500
- Come, sit down.
- Come, quickly.

441
00:18:19,500 --> 00:18:20,580
- It's just in time for dinner.
- Sit.

442
00:18:20,580 --> 00:18:21,670
- It smells so good.
- What a coincidence.

443
00:18:21,670 --> 00:18:23,630
- Get a bowl.
- You're lucky, Hui.

444
00:18:23,630 --> 00:18:25,150
You're back whenever there's good food.

445
00:18:25,150 --> 00:18:25,990
Come on.

446
00:18:26,520 --> 00:18:27,390
Here.

447
00:18:27,390 --> 00:18:28,230
Thanks, Mr. Chen.

448
00:18:29,430 --> 00:18:31,300
Such a feast today.

449
00:18:31,300 --> 00:18:33,340
Today's dishes were all made by your dad.

450
00:18:35,190 --> 00:18:36,630
Dad, did I interrupt something?

451
00:18:38,540 --> 00:18:40,430
You didn't interrupt me,

452
00:18:40,430 --> 00:18:41,340
but maybe we

453
00:18:41,340 --> 00:18:42,780
interrupted something of yours?

454
00:18:43,920 --> 00:18:46,300
Actually, I really do have something
I want to tell you all.

455
00:18:46,300 --> 00:18:47,800
There, you see?

456
00:18:47,800 --> 00:18:48,670
Speak.

457
00:18:48,670 --> 00:18:50,040
Songge and I

458
00:18:50,040 --> 00:18:50,950
plan to

459
00:18:50,950 --> 00:18:52,300
sell the roller skating rink.

460
00:18:53,150 --> 00:18:55,300
We're going to the city
to open an internet cafe.

461
00:18:56,100 --> 00:18:56,950
Internet cafes?

462
00:18:57,820 --> 00:18:59,190
What's an internet cafe?

463
00:18:59,190 --> 00:19:01,780
It's a place where young people chat
and play games online.

464
00:19:01,780 --> 00:19:02,710
They're very popular now.

465
00:19:02,710 --> 00:19:05,260
Right. And there's only one
in the city right now.

466
00:19:05,260 --> 00:19:06,150
If we go there,

467
00:19:06,150 --> 00:19:07,340
we can get a head start.

468
00:19:10,190 --> 00:19:11,470
You're going to the city?

469
00:19:11,470 --> 00:19:13,190
So suddenly?

470
00:19:13,190 --> 00:19:14,340
In the future,

471
00:19:14,340 --> 00:19:16,060
won't it be inconvenient to come home?

472
00:19:16,060 --> 00:19:16,950
Mrs. Chen,

473
00:19:16,950 --> 00:19:18,630
we'll still come back often.

474
00:19:18,630 --> 00:19:19,910
This is our home.

475
00:19:19,910 --> 00:19:20,950
Yeah, Mom.

476
00:19:20,950 --> 00:19:21,870
Don't you worry.

477
00:19:32,630 --> 00:19:33,470
Dad,

478
00:19:33,670 --> 00:19:35,190
you made Mom angry earlier?

479
00:19:35,190 --> 00:19:36,950
Nonsense, I've been
trying to cheer her up.

480
00:19:41,780 --> 00:19:42,620
Mom,

481
00:19:43,500 --> 00:19:44,710
are you angry?

482
00:19:48,390 --> 00:19:49,580
I'm not angry.

483
00:19:49,580 --> 00:19:51,500
I'm just a little out of my element.

484
00:19:51,500 --> 00:19:52,540
It's so sudden.

485
00:19:53,190 --> 00:19:54,910
But you two are grown-ups now.

486
00:19:54,910 --> 00:19:55,760
You can't stay

487
00:19:55,770 --> 00:19:57,390
in this small town forever.

488
00:19:57,390 --> 00:19:58,520
It's right for you to go out.

489
00:20:00,090 --> 00:20:00,950
This

490
00:20:00,950 --> 00:20:02,950
is a bit of savings
from your dad and me.

491
00:20:02,950 --> 00:20:05,260
Opening an internet cafe
will require money.

492
00:20:05,260 --> 00:20:06,300
It's not much,

493
00:20:06,300 --> 00:20:07,580
but it can help for a while.

494
00:20:07,590 --> 00:20:08,440
No, Mom.

495
00:20:08,450 --> 00:20:09,870
Please take the money back.

496
00:20:09,870 --> 00:20:11,300
The money from selling the rink

497
00:20:11,300 --> 00:20:12,150
is enough.

498
00:20:12,160 --> 00:20:13,030
Could you sell

499
00:20:13,050 --> 00:20:14,670
the roller skating rink that quickly?

500
00:20:14,670 --> 00:20:15,580
Yes.

501
00:20:15,580 --> 00:20:17,060
The day I went to the police station
to close the case,

502
00:20:17,060 --> 00:20:18,300
I ran into Mr. Tong.

503
00:20:18,300 --> 00:20:20,260
I told him I wanted to sell the rink.

504
00:20:20,260 --> 00:20:21,120
He said his niece

505
00:20:21,130 --> 00:20:22,580
happened to want to start a business.

506
00:20:22,580 --> 00:20:24,150
We even settled on a price.

507
00:20:25,120 --> 00:20:27,190
No matter how much you get
for the roller skating rink,

508
00:20:27,190 --> 00:20:28,870
that's your own money.

509
00:20:28,870 --> 00:20:30,390
This is from your dad and me.

510
00:20:30,390 --> 00:20:31,340
You must take it.

511
00:20:31,340 --> 00:20:32,180
Mom...

512
00:20:32,470 --> 00:20:33,830
- Take it.
- Just take it.

513
00:20:34,190 --> 00:20:35,030
Take it.

514
00:20:35,780 --> 00:20:37,060
It's good that young people

515
00:20:37,060 --> 00:20:38,060
have ambitions.

516
00:20:38,670 --> 00:20:39,700
Your mom and I

517
00:20:39,700 --> 00:20:41,260
wish you a successful opening.

518
00:20:42,390 --> 00:20:43,230
Thanks, Mom.

519
00:20:43,230 --> 00:20:44,230
Thanks, Mrs. Chen.

520
00:20:44,230 --> 00:20:45,070
Thanks, Mr. Chen.

521
00:20:46,260 --> 00:20:47,340
Hey, Hui,

522
00:20:47,340 --> 00:20:48,990
once your internet cafe opens,

523
00:20:49,230 --> 00:20:51,540
you must invite me to take a look.

524
00:20:51,540 --> 00:20:53,210
Let me see something new.

525
00:20:53,230 --> 00:20:54,540
Of course I'll take you to see it.

526
00:20:55,230 --> 00:20:56,260
We've talked enough.

527
00:20:56,260 --> 00:20:57,100
Eat quickly.

528
00:20:57,100 --> 00:20:58,990
Look, the food is getting cold.

529
00:20:58,990 --> 00:21:00,420
Come on, eat.

530
00:21:00,990 --> 00:21:02,190
Try it.

531
00:21:02,190 --> 00:21:03,190
Try your dad's cooking.

532
00:21:03,710 --> 00:21:04,820
Try it.

533
00:21:22,630 --> 00:21:23,670
I'll wash them.

534
00:21:24,260 --> 00:21:25,630
No need, go rest.

535
00:21:28,630 --> 00:21:29,990
Before dinner,

536
00:21:29,990 --> 00:21:31,740
what was it you wanted to tell me?

537
00:21:33,060 --> 00:21:34,780
It was nothing.

538
00:21:35,540 --> 00:21:36,580
Well, I gave you a chance.

539
00:21:36,580 --> 00:21:37,710
If you won't say it, I'm leaving.

540
00:21:37,710 --> 00:21:38,780
Wait.

541
00:21:42,190 --> 00:21:43,910
There is actually something

542
00:21:43,910 --> 00:21:45,230
I need to discuss with you.

543
00:21:45,230 --> 00:21:46,070
Go ahead.

544
00:21:47,500 --> 00:21:48,910
The suspect in the case

545
00:21:48,910 --> 00:21:49,950
I'm working on

546
00:21:50,990 --> 00:21:51,870
is on the run.

547
00:21:51,870 --> 00:21:54,580
The municipal PSB has also
been putting a lot of pressure on me.

548
00:21:55,540 --> 00:21:56,380
They say this person

549
00:21:57,150 --> 00:21:58,710
is closely connected

550
00:21:58,710 --> 00:22:00,100
to Gao Ying's death back then.

551
00:22:00,100 --> 00:22:01,870
So the municipal PSB has decided

552
00:22:01,870 --> 00:22:04,150
to conduct an autopsy

553
00:22:04,150 --> 00:22:04,990
on Gao Ying.

554
00:22:08,670 --> 00:22:10,100
So this is what was waiting for me.

555
00:22:10,100 --> 00:22:11,950
No, I'm reporting it to you.

556
00:22:11,950 --> 00:22:12,910
Consider it

557
00:22:12,910 --> 00:22:14,630
a heads-up in advance.

558
00:22:17,260 --> 00:22:18,190
Go on.

559
00:22:18,990 --> 00:22:19,910
Done,

560
00:22:19,910 --> 00:22:20,750
that's all.

561
00:22:25,390 --> 00:22:27,100
Chen Hongbing, what are you trying to do?

562
00:22:27,700 --> 00:22:28,540
It's my job.

563
00:22:28,540 --> 00:22:29,630
After all these years,

564
00:22:29,630 --> 00:22:31,470
have you ever considered my perspective?

565
00:22:33,430 --> 00:22:34,740
Ding Yue, no...

566
00:22:34,740 --> 00:22:36,470
No matter what I do,

567
00:22:36,470 --> 00:22:39,390
I've always looked at things
from your point of view.

568
00:22:39,390 --> 00:22:40,300
Back then,

569
00:22:40,300 --> 00:22:41,780
I was the one who proposed marriage.

570
00:22:41,780 --> 00:22:43,340
My parents didn't approve.

571
00:22:43,340 --> 00:22:44,990
I nearly cut ties with my family

572
00:22:44,990 --> 00:22:46,300
just to be with you.

573
00:22:47,150 --> 00:22:48,060
Over the years,

574
00:22:48,060 --> 00:22:49,150
I gave birth to Hui,

575
00:22:49,150 --> 00:22:50,780
helped you lay your mother to rest,

576
00:22:50,780 --> 00:22:52,740
and cared for your father day and night.

577
00:22:53,320 --> 00:22:55,580
Even if I don't get credit,
at least recognize my hard work,

578
00:22:55,580 --> 00:22:57,100
- Chen Hongbing?
- Yes.

579
00:22:57,100 --> 00:22:59,260
Is there any room in your heart for me?

580
00:22:59,820 --> 00:23:01,230
How could there not be?

581
00:23:01,780 --> 00:23:02,780
I'm telling you,

582
00:23:02,780 --> 00:23:03,950
for all these years,

583
00:23:03,950 --> 00:23:05,630
your place in my heart

584
00:23:05,630 --> 00:23:07,500
has always been the most important.

585
00:23:07,500 --> 00:23:08,740
Don't give me that.

586
00:23:08,740 --> 00:23:10,580
Did I say you
couldn't investigate Gao Ying?

587
00:23:10,580 --> 00:23:12,580
That day when you were looking for
that little broken box,

588
00:23:12,580 --> 00:23:13,740
didn't I give it to you?

589
00:23:13,740 --> 00:23:15,670
What did you actually find?

590
00:23:15,670 --> 00:23:17,500
Now, they have stopped
the investigation.

591
00:23:17,500 --> 00:23:18,430
What are you trying to do?

592
00:23:18,430 --> 00:23:19,300
Exhume the body?

593
00:23:19,300 --> 00:23:20,500
Announce it to the world?

594
00:23:20,500 --> 00:23:22,950
So that all of Fengyang Town
knows about this?

595
00:23:23,740 --> 00:23:25,190
How romantic of you.

596
00:23:25,190 --> 00:23:26,260
A deputy director

597
00:23:26,260 --> 00:23:27,540
reopens a cold case

598
00:23:27,540 --> 00:23:28,870
for his former fiancée.

599
00:23:28,870 --> 00:23:30,260
It's so touching.

600
00:23:30,260 --> 00:23:32,670
So, should I set off fireworks
to celebrate for you?

601
00:23:35,020 --> 00:23:35,870
Look at you.

602
00:23:39,150 --> 00:23:40,340
Ding Yue, listen to me.

603
00:23:43,630 --> 00:23:44,670
Ding Yue,

604
00:23:44,670 --> 00:23:45,870
you and Gao Ying

605
00:23:45,870 --> 00:23:47,340
were best friends back then.

606
00:23:48,390 --> 00:23:50,630
Gao Ying has been gone for many years.

607
00:23:50,630 --> 00:23:53,020
The things between her and me

608
00:23:53,020 --> 00:23:54,670
are long in the past.

609
00:23:54,670 --> 00:23:55,570
Now,

610
00:23:55,590 --> 00:23:56,780
you are my wife,

611
00:23:56,780 --> 00:23:58,340
but I am still a police officer.

612
00:23:58,340 --> 00:23:59,950
From a professional standpoint,

613
00:24:00,990 --> 00:24:02,390
I find this case

614
00:24:02,390 --> 00:24:04,230
truly suspicious.

615
00:24:04,230 --> 00:24:05,870
Don't use those high-sounding excuses.

616
00:24:05,870 --> 00:24:08,100
Listen to me.
Since the municipal PSB is here

617
00:24:08,100 --> 00:24:09,150
to investigate this,

618
00:24:09,150 --> 00:24:10,540
I want to use this chance

619
00:24:10,540 --> 00:24:11,390
to get to the bottom

620
00:24:11,390 --> 00:24:12,260
of this case.

621
00:24:12,260 --> 00:24:13,740
Isn't that giving Gao Ying closure too?

622
00:24:13,740 --> 00:24:15,500
Have you considered me?

623
00:24:15,500 --> 00:24:18,150
Have you thought about me?

624
00:24:18,150 --> 00:24:20,710
Do you know what
people outside say about me?

625
00:24:20,710 --> 00:24:23,020
They say Chen Hongbing's fiancée

626
00:24:23,020 --> 00:24:23,950
was Gao Ying.

627
00:24:24,950 --> 00:24:26,740
I'm nothing but a replacement.

628
00:24:26,740 --> 00:24:28,340
Do you understand? A replacement!

629
00:24:28,950 --> 00:24:30,540
After all these years,

630
00:24:30,540 --> 00:24:32,340
I thought

631
00:24:32,340 --> 00:24:33,260
I must have finally

632
00:24:33,260 --> 00:24:35,990
warmed your heart.

633
00:24:35,990 --> 00:24:37,500
I didn't expect

634
00:24:37,500 --> 00:24:39,780
that your heart
still only holds Gao Ying.

635
00:24:39,780 --> 00:24:40,990
Fine.

636
00:24:40,990 --> 00:24:42,060
Stop crying.

637
00:24:42,060 --> 00:24:42,900
Don't be sad.

638
00:24:44,260 --> 00:24:45,870
If you're against it,

639
00:24:45,870 --> 00:24:46,990
I won't go through with it.

640
00:24:46,990 --> 00:24:49,060
For you, as long as it makes you happy,

641
00:24:49,060 --> 00:24:50,670
I'd even quit the police force.

642
00:24:51,990 --> 00:24:53,780
- I will retire.
- Why would you quit?

643
00:24:53,780 --> 00:24:55,990
Did I ever say
I didn't want you to be a cop?

644
00:24:55,990 --> 00:24:57,870
You've been a cop all these years,

645
00:24:57,870 --> 00:24:59,190
neglecting the home and the kids.

646
00:24:59,190 --> 00:25:00,910
Have I ever complained?

647
00:25:00,910 --> 00:25:02,150
What did I even say?

648
00:25:02,150 --> 00:25:03,470
What kind of person do you take me for?

649
00:25:03,470 --> 00:25:04,820
What are you trying to say?

650
00:25:04,820 --> 00:25:06,780
Isn't it because I'm a cop
that I have to do this?

651
00:25:06,780 --> 00:25:07,650
If you weren't a cop,

652
00:25:07,650 --> 00:25:08,710
could you even do this?

653
00:25:08,710 --> 00:25:09,990
But you won't let me do my job.

654
00:25:09,990 --> 00:25:11,870
Tell me, then, how am I supposed
to be a cop?

655
00:25:11,870 --> 00:25:12,730
You...

656
00:25:12,740 --> 00:25:13,740
Fine, investigate.

657
00:25:13,740 --> 00:25:14,720
Go ahead and investigate!

658
00:25:18,870 --> 00:25:19,710
Ding Yue,

659
00:25:20,260 --> 00:25:21,430
what did you just say?

660
00:25:22,540 --> 00:25:23,710
You told me to investigate.

661
00:25:23,710 --> 00:25:25,100
I did not.

662
00:25:25,100 --> 00:25:27,390
I just heard you say "investigate",

663
00:25:27,390 --> 00:25:28,230
right?

664
00:25:29,020 --> 00:25:30,340
Alright, that's enough.

665
00:25:32,150 --> 00:25:33,100
Sorry.

666
00:25:33,100 --> 00:25:34,390
Listen.

667
00:25:34,390 --> 00:25:35,230
Honey,

668
00:25:35,710 --> 00:25:37,390
with your level of awareness,

669
00:25:37,390 --> 00:25:39,390
you should be
the director at our station.

670
00:25:39,390 --> 00:25:41,340
You'd be way better than Director Tong.

671
00:25:41,340 --> 00:25:42,180
Don't you think?

672
00:25:43,150 --> 00:25:44,580
Knock it off.

673
00:25:44,580 --> 00:25:45,430
I'm telling you,

674
00:25:45,430 --> 00:25:46,470
just this once.

675
00:25:47,150 --> 00:25:48,190
Thank you.

676
00:25:48,780 --> 00:25:50,100
Stop crying now.

677
00:25:50,100 --> 00:25:51,020
Come on.

678
00:25:51,020 --> 00:25:52,470
It's my fault.

679
00:25:52,470 --> 00:25:53,670
Here.

680
00:25:53,670 --> 00:25:54,580
Have some water.

681
00:25:56,780 --> 00:25:57,820
Alright.

682
00:26:02,710 --> 00:26:05,820
Choose an auspicious time
to break ground.

683
00:26:05,820 --> 00:26:09,390
Offer a stick of incense.

684
00:26:09,390 --> 00:26:11,470
Lift the coffin!

685
00:26:38,630 --> 00:26:39,470
Tang.

686
00:27:08,780 --> 00:27:09,870
What's wrong with Chief Liu?

687
00:27:10,660 --> 00:27:11,500
I'll go check on her.

688
00:27:11,500 --> 00:27:12,340
Okay.

689
00:27:19,430 --> 00:27:20,270
Officer Liu.

690
00:27:22,630 --> 00:27:23,820
Officer Liu, are you alright?

691
00:27:24,670 --> 00:27:26,260
The medicine... In the car...

692
00:27:26,260 --> 00:27:27,340
Medicine...

693
00:28:11,630 --> 00:28:12,630
You saw everything.

694
00:28:14,150 --> 00:28:15,990
I'm sorry, I didn't mean to.

695
00:28:17,260 --> 00:28:18,150
It's not your fault.

696
00:28:22,190 --> 00:28:23,030
Officer Liu,

697
00:28:23,580 --> 00:28:25,430
is it because of chemotherapy that you...

698
00:28:28,740 --> 00:28:29,580
Songge,

699
00:28:30,540 --> 00:28:31,710
don't tell anyone.

700
00:28:32,450 --> 00:28:33,300
Don't worry.

701
00:28:33,300 --> 00:28:34,630
I won't tell a soul.

702
00:28:35,870 --> 00:28:37,100
If it were possible,

703
00:28:37,780 --> 00:28:38,650
I wouldn't want

704
00:28:38,660 --> 00:28:39,780
anyone to know I'm sick.

705
00:28:42,260 --> 00:28:43,190
Thank you.

706
00:28:47,060 --> 00:28:47,900
Officer Liu,

707
00:28:48,470 --> 00:28:49,390
the way you are now,

708
00:28:49,390 --> 00:28:50,810
shouldn't you be getting some rest?

709
00:28:53,300 --> 00:28:54,340
It's stage three lymphoma.

710
00:28:55,430 --> 00:28:56,670
I don't have much time left.

711
00:28:58,230 --> 00:28:59,340
Songge,

712
00:28:59,340 --> 00:29:00,260
I'm already very lucky

713
00:29:00,260 --> 00:29:01,340
that I still have the chance

714
00:29:01,340 --> 00:29:02,340
to do what I want to do.

715
00:29:03,630 --> 00:29:04,780
You don't need to pity me.

716
00:29:06,500 --> 00:29:07,340
Officer Liu,

717
00:29:08,630 --> 00:29:09,710
aren't you afraid?

718
00:29:12,950 --> 00:29:14,780
Everyone's destination is the same.

719
00:29:15,710 --> 00:29:17,300
It's just a matter of distance.

720
00:29:19,390 --> 00:29:20,700
But as long as you can still run,

721
00:29:21,820 --> 00:29:23,100
there's nothing to be afraid of.

722
00:29:24,580 --> 00:29:25,820
As long as I can still run.

723
00:29:28,190 --> 00:29:29,030
Songge,

724
00:29:30,420 --> 00:29:32,190
don't just keep your eyes
on the finish line.

725
00:29:34,920 --> 00:29:36,230
You still have a long road ahead.

726
00:29:43,950 --> 00:29:44,820
Songge,

727
00:29:44,820 --> 00:29:46,740
I rented a place near the internet cafe.

728
00:29:46,740 --> 00:29:49,110
It's not far from the hospital,
and it even has a courtyard.

729
00:29:53,430 --> 00:29:54,270
We're here.

730
00:30:00,300 --> 00:30:01,470
What do you think?

731
00:30:01,470 --> 00:30:03,500
This is the courtyard I told you about.

732
00:30:03,500 --> 00:30:04,680
It's really nice.

733
00:30:04,930 --> 00:30:06,500
If we tidy it up a bit,

734
00:30:06,500 --> 00:30:07,910
it'll look beautiful.

735
00:30:07,910 --> 00:30:08,750
Yeah.

736
00:30:09,740 --> 00:30:11,230
In this flower bed,

737
00:30:11,230 --> 00:30:13,300
I'm going to plant
all my favorite flowers.

738
00:30:13,300 --> 00:30:14,260
I'll plant

739
00:30:14,260 --> 00:30:15,470
hydrangeas,

740
00:30:15,470 --> 00:30:16,740
Chinese roses,

741
00:30:16,740 --> 00:30:17,740
bellflowers,

742
00:30:17,740 --> 00:30:18,970
and cherry tomatoes.

743
00:30:20,060 --> 00:30:21,390
And also...

744
00:30:21,390 --> 00:30:22,230
And you.

745
00:30:22,440 --> 00:30:24,100
I'll plant you here, too.

746
00:30:31,500 --> 00:30:34,420
(Yingxiong Internet Cafe)

747
00:30:41,190 --> 00:30:43,470
Chen Hui, come over here for a second.

748
00:30:45,780 --> 00:30:46,620
Close your eyes.

749
00:30:50,870 --> 00:30:51,750
Okay.

750
00:30:51,760 --> 00:30:52,750
You can open them now.

751
00:30:55,020 --> 00:30:55,880
How?

752
00:30:55,900 --> 00:30:56,750
Does it look good?

753
00:30:57,580 --> 00:30:58,420
It looks great.

754
00:31:01,820 --> 00:31:02,660
Thank you.

755
00:31:03,630 --> 00:31:04,580
It was nothing.

756
00:31:05,820 --> 00:31:07,540
This is our new beginning.

757
00:31:07,540 --> 00:31:09,660
(Yingxiong)

758
00:31:13,190 --> 00:31:15,870
I'll do it.

759
00:31:15,870 --> 00:31:17,230
Dad,

760
00:31:17,230 --> 00:31:18,300
take a break.

761
00:31:18,300 --> 00:31:19,670
Just watch from here.

762
00:31:20,000 --> 00:31:20,920
Come on.

763
00:31:21,200 --> 00:31:22,210
All right, here we go.

764
00:31:23,300 --> 00:31:24,500
What's all this fuss about now?

765
00:31:25,240 --> 00:31:26,150
Let me do it.

766
00:31:26,150 --> 00:31:26,990
Dad, let me.

767
00:31:26,990 --> 00:31:28,670
- I can manage.
- Just sit down. Sit down.

768
00:31:28,670 --> 00:31:29,740
Isn't this the stuff from

769
00:31:29,740 --> 00:31:30,670
when Hui was sick?

770
00:31:30,670 --> 00:31:33,060
It's an eyesore and takes up space,
so I'm clearing it all out.

771
00:31:33,060 --> 00:31:34,230
It's good to get it tidied up.

772
00:31:41,230 --> 00:31:42,080
Tang.

773
00:31:42,100 --> 00:31:42,940
Director Chen.

774
00:31:43,920 --> 00:31:45,580
I'm here to update you
on Gao Ying's case.

775
00:31:45,590 --> 00:31:46,430
Over here.

776
00:31:46,820 --> 00:31:48,740
Gao Ying's autopsy results
are out, right?

777
00:31:48,740 --> 00:31:49,580
Yes.

778
00:31:49,580 --> 00:31:51,230
Although the body was buried for so long

779
00:31:51,230 --> 00:31:52,950
that much evidence
was destroyed biologically,

780
00:31:52,950 --> 00:31:54,230
we found a powder

781
00:31:54,230 --> 00:31:56,060
on the body,
and it's potassium manganate.

782
00:31:56,060 --> 00:31:57,540
It's the same substance found on

783
00:31:57,540 --> 00:31:58,740
Yu Susu and Lu Yuan's bodies.

784
00:31:59,230 --> 00:32:00,300
That's wonderful news.

785
00:32:01,500 --> 00:32:02,340
Tang,

786
00:32:02,710 --> 00:32:05,070
what does the municipal PSB think
about merging the cases?

787
00:32:05,190 --> 00:32:06,060
The municipal PSB says

788
00:32:06,060 --> 00:32:07,580
there's now direct
physical evidence linking

789
00:32:07,580 --> 00:32:08,910
Gao Ying's case to Huo Kaiming's case.

790
00:32:08,910 --> 00:32:10,740
We can start the process
of merging the cases.

791
00:32:11,230 --> 00:32:12,070
Tang,

792
00:32:12,500 --> 00:32:13,340
thank you.

793
00:32:13,340 --> 00:32:14,180
Alright.

794
00:32:17,950 --> 00:32:19,470
Go and get that mutton stewing.

795
00:32:19,470 --> 00:32:20,310
I have good news.

796
00:32:20,500 --> 00:32:21,470
What good news?

797
00:32:22,510 --> 00:32:24,780
Gao Ying's autopsy results are out.

798
00:32:24,780 --> 00:32:26,300
It wasn't spontaneous combustion.

799
00:32:26,410 --> 00:32:27,670
We finally found evidence,

800
00:32:27,680 --> 00:32:28,780
so we can merge the cases.

801
00:32:28,800 --> 00:32:29,990
That really is good news.

802
00:32:29,990 --> 00:32:31,580
All right. I'll go stew the mutton.

803
00:32:31,580 --> 00:32:32,420
Okay.

804
00:32:32,670 --> 00:32:33,540
Dad,

805
00:32:33,540 --> 00:32:34,780
we're having mutton tonight.

806
00:32:36,020 --> 00:32:36,990
Good.

807
00:32:36,990 --> 00:32:37,830
Dad,

808
00:32:38,190 --> 00:32:39,030
let's go inside.

809
00:32:39,740 --> 00:32:40,580
Let's go in.

810
00:32:42,340 --> 00:32:44,630
Tell me,
has that criminal been caught yet?

811
00:32:44,790 --> 00:32:46,540
We are still

812
00:32:46,540 --> 00:32:47,430
after the criminal.

813
00:32:48,560 --> 00:32:49,430
Catching a criminal

814
00:32:49,430 --> 00:32:50,870
is like flying a kite.

815
00:32:50,870 --> 00:32:53,260
The stronger the wind,
the more you have to let out the line.

816
00:32:53,260 --> 00:32:54,100
That's what they call

817
00:32:54,110 --> 00:32:55,510
"balancing tension and relaxation".

818
00:32:56,100 --> 00:32:58,710
Otherwise, the kite string will break.

819
00:32:58,710 --> 00:32:59,630
What you're describing

820
00:32:59,630 --> 00:33:00,820
is how to catch a fish.

821
00:33:03,990 --> 00:33:04,990
I told you

822
00:33:04,990 --> 00:33:06,150
I would definitely

823
00:33:06,330 --> 00:33:07,910
get to the bottom of this case.

824
00:33:07,910 --> 00:33:08,750
See?

825
00:33:09,630 --> 00:33:10,910
That's for sure.

826
00:33:10,910 --> 00:33:12,820
When it comes to cases,
you've never been wrong.

827
00:33:13,570 --> 00:33:14,740
You certainly have a good eye.

828
00:33:15,390 --> 00:33:16,430
Enough.

829
00:33:16,430 --> 00:33:17,670
Anymore praise will be too much.

830
00:33:21,020 --> 00:33:22,100
Why do I feel like

831
00:33:22,870 --> 00:33:24,300
you've put on weight lately?

832
00:33:25,470 --> 00:33:26,310
That's impossible.

833
00:33:27,260 --> 00:33:28,710
The case isn't solved yet.

834
00:33:28,710 --> 00:33:29,910
How could I get fat?

835
00:33:33,230 --> 00:33:34,100
I remember back then,

836
00:33:34,100 --> 00:33:36,260
when I first met you,

837
00:33:36,260 --> 00:33:37,500
you looked quite fit.

838
00:33:38,630 --> 00:33:39,980
Don't dwell on past glories.

839
00:33:42,230 --> 00:33:43,500
In those days,

840
00:33:43,500 --> 00:33:45,300
you wore your hair in two small braids.

841
00:33:45,300 --> 00:33:46,470
It was really quite pretty.

842
00:33:47,150 --> 00:33:48,260
You still remember it?

843
00:33:48,260 --> 00:33:49,300
How could I forget?

844
00:33:51,100 --> 00:33:52,670
That feels like

845
00:33:52,670 --> 00:33:54,710
it was over 20 years ago.

846
00:33:57,340 --> 00:33:58,180
Hey, girl.

847
00:33:58,870 --> 00:34:01,470
Let me have a look
at your Chairman Mao badge.

848
00:34:01,470 --> 00:34:02,330
Let us borrow it

849
00:34:02,330 --> 00:34:03,340
and see it.

850
00:34:03,780 --> 00:34:04,740
What are you doing?

851
00:34:04,740 --> 00:34:05,700
- What are we doing?
- What are we doing?

852
00:34:05,710 --> 00:34:07,020
Just give it here!

853
00:34:07,470 --> 00:34:08,350
What are you doing?

854
00:34:08,350 --> 00:34:09,540
Stop!

855
00:34:09,540 --> 00:34:10,380
Stop.

856
00:34:12,180 --> 00:34:13,020
You're asking for it!

857
00:34:16,350 --> 00:34:18,140
Give it back! Move!

858
00:34:18,140 --> 00:34:18,990
You're so bold.

859
00:34:18,990 --> 00:34:19,830
Move it!

860
00:34:21,540 --> 00:34:22,390
Get lost!

861
00:34:22,530 --> 00:34:23,510
What the heck?

862
00:34:24,700 --> 00:34:25,540
Are you okay?

863
00:34:25,950 --> 00:34:26,790
I'm fine.

864
00:34:27,350 --> 00:34:28,190
Thank you.

865
00:34:45,310 --> 00:34:46,170
Wait a second.

866
00:34:46,180 --> 00:34:47,070
Do you still remember?

867
00:34:47,990 --> 00:34:49,270
Back then, Gao Ying

868
00:34:50,020 --> 00:34:51,660
always had this rainbow glow
on her head.

869
00:34:52,660 --> 00:34:53,790
When the sun hit it,

870
00:34:53,790 --> 00:34:54,700
it was all colorful.

871
00:34:54,700 --> 00:34:55,540
It looked quite nice.

872
00:34:56,830 --> 00:34:57,670
I don't remember.

873
00:34:59,870 --> 00:35:00,710
Are you angry?

874
00:35:02,620 --> 00:35:03,700
I was just asking.

875
00:35:03,700 --> 00:35:04,540
What's wrong?

876
00:35:05,970 --> 00:35:06,830
Yes.

877
00:35:06,830 --> 00:35:08,020
Back then, she often had

878
00:35:08,020 --> 00:35:09,100
a glow or something

879
00:35:09,100 --> 00:35:11,100
in her hair or on her body.

880
00:35:11,100 --> 00:35:13,020
I asked her about it once later.

881
00:35:13,020 --> 00:35:14,040
She said

882
00:35:14,060 --> 00:35:14,950
it was because her dad

883
00:35:14,970 --> 00:35:16,990
worked at the old coal washing plant.

884
00:35:16,990 --> 00:35:19,310
She used to go there often
to bring him meals.

885
00:35:19,310 --> 00:35:20,870
Every time she came back from that,

886
00:35:20,870 --> 00:35:22,060
on her body

887
00:35:22,060 --> 00:35:23,870
and in her hair,
there would be that glow.

888
00:35:23,870 --> 00:35:25,580
It seemed to be

889
00:35:25,580 --> 00:35:27,470
from the water in the coal washing pool.

890
00:35:30,140 --> 00:35:31,580
The old coal washing plant.

891
00:35:45,740 --> 00:35:55,540
(Heyi Coal Washing Plant, Fengyang Town)

892
00:36:16,750 --> 00:36:17,590
What's this?

893
00:36:23,470 --> 00:36:24,310
A motorcycle.

894
00:36:29,220 --> 00:36:30,180
It looks a lot like

895
00:36:30,180 --> 00:36:31,350
the one Ma Heping described.

896
00:36:32,950 --> 00:36:34,430
Is it the scarred woman's?

897
00:36:34,430 --> 00:36:35,620
Very likely.

898
00:36:35,620 --> 00:36:36,500
Go.

899
00:36:36,500 --> 00:36:37,340
Take a look around.

900
00:37:07,910 --> 00:37:08,750
Quickly.

901
00:37:09,470 --> 00:37:10,310
Go find a pole.

902
00:37:10,870 --> 00:37:11,710
Okay.

903
00:37:21,220 --> 00:37:22,700
Director Chen.

904
00:37:34,180 --> 00:37:35,310
There's something underneath.

905
00:37:37,220 --> 00:37:38,540
It's quite heavy.

906
00:37:38,540 --> 00:37:39,380
Give me a hand.

907
00:37:44,390 --> 00:37:45,230
Open it up and see.

908
00:37:53,350 --> 00:37:54,310
There's another layer.

909
00:38:03,430 --> 00:38:04,270
It's cough syrup.

910
00:38:04,860 --> 00:38:07,700
(Peidun Cough Syrup)

911
00:38:07,700 --> 00:38:08,830
It's full of them.
